| Instruction                                     | Description                             |
| ----------------------------------------------- | --------------------------------------- |
| `JMP addr`                                      | Unconditional jump                      |
| `JSR addr`                                      | Jump to subroutine (push PC-1 on stack) |
| `RTS`                                           | Return from subroutine                  |
| `BCC / BCS / BEQ / BNE / BMI / BPL / BVC / BVS` | Conditional branches based on P flags   |
